snippet.title: Low Blow (PC/DOS) 1990, EA, Synergistic Software
snippet.description: Low Blow is a beyond-the-rules boxing game where illegal hits are, in fact, legal. Landing a punch in someone's genitals is not only a legal move in this game, it's also quite effective. You can play a tournament against the computer or a simple game against your friends.
